    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Parmi les r&#xE9;sultats obtenus jusqu&#x2019;en ao&#xFB;t 2020 : 1) inclusion accrue des consid&#xE9;rations LGBTI dans la strat&#xE9;gie d&#x2019;&#xE9;coute plurielle de la Commission V&#xE9;rit&#xE9; colombienne suite &#xE0; l&#x2019;adoption de recommandations par la Commission V&#xE9;rit&#xE9;; 2) reconnaissance publique accrue par la Commission V&#xE9;rit&#xE9; colombienne des violations commises contre les victimes LGBTI du conflit.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results achieved as of August 2020 include: (1) increased inclusion of LGBTI considerations in the Colombian Truth Commission&#x2019;s Plural Listening Strategy further to the adoption of recommendations by the Truth Commission; and (2) increased public recognition by the Colombian Truth Commission of the violations committed against LGBTI victims of the conflict.</narrative>
    </description>
   </indicator>
