     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Les r&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s de ce projet comprennent :  1)  une participation accrue et significative des personnes LGBTI aux efforts de consolidation de la paix; 2) l&apos;am&#xE9;lioration des r&#xE9;ponses des institutions de l&apos;Etat et de la soci&#xE9;t&#xE9; aux droits des personnes et communaut&#xE9;s LGBTI.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">The expected outcomes for this project include:  (1) enhanced meaningful participation of LGBTI people in peace-building efforts; and  (2) improved responses of state institutions and society to the rights of LGBTI persons and communities.</narrative>
